{"tid":163390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友像刺蝟","createTime":"2017-03-20T02:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T04:09:08.000Z","uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b4ef58a3709572717b2b7187bc0bc018b0739d","tid":163390,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n女朋友過去有好多陰影 絕對唔簡單 <br />\n佢成日都訓唔到 諗起舊時會唔開心<br />\n作為男朋友都好擔心佢健康 精神狀況<br />\n但偏偏我就無乜野可以做到 除左陪佢 有時都會有D內疚<br />\n而佢有時會講某D說話<br />\n而果D說話真係會令我好心痛<br />\n雖然我知道佢係愛我 佢好怕失去我<br />\n但另一方面又覺得 佢傷害我 <br />\n佢可以話係一隻刺蝟  捉得太緊會刺傷<br />\n究竟我可以點樣做 定係只要簡單陪住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34005ac618185a060c5dd04f9013cf7b2b18432c","tid":163390,"uid":82427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:50:49.000Z","msg":"舊事咩事唔開心先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff10e2dc1cab09570468240fb887a8194909056","tid":163390,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:53:53.000Z","msg":"我知道唔可以係佢面前表現得唔開心 <br />\n因為兩個都唔開心 最後佢只會更唔開心<br />\n我已經會表現堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6d48af421dec7c8bb352e97bd5de6b14d95a18","tid":163390,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊事咩事唔開心先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前男友 學校 家庭"},{"pid":"f6dd53c990522f5c09e44e04d52765243dba0b35","tid":163390,"uid":46608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>舊事咩事唔開心先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前男友 學校 家庭</blockquote><br />\n咁似我ex既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb6b9c438841ed17296b2ea739c3058df5ee1ad","tid":163390,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>舊事咩事唔開心先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前男友 學校 家庭</blockquote><br />\n咁似我ex既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世界上總有同一類人架啦 CHING"},{"pid":"990255b2f4902c1ebfe6e6a24c6f92526e3b29f1","tid":163390,"uid":82427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"你女友係咪本身就係悲觀嘅人？<br />\n如果係嘅話依啲人好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f193e109d935c2068278c3c0acbbf4685dc9d0f0","tid":163390,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你女友係咪本身就係悲觀嘅人？<br />\n如果係嘅話依啲人好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔算好悲觀 有時會好開心 <br />\n不過唔開心果陣 一個人果陣就會好倔強 轉牛角尖"},{"pid":"d3b04e2846de75939a5c340d43ead53baadad1dc","tid":163390,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"唔洗太痴身 唔洗特登諗話幫佢做啲咩<br />\n得閒比佢發泄吓<br />\n陪住佢就得"},{"pid":"670c7701d529935acd868d0213e13a8dee6a758f","tid":163390,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:03:18.000Z","msg":"刺蝟好無食"},{"pid":"789d1b21b0c8a890bad5fc5208ac2d6f917a94f7","tid":163390,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:04:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36ac909dbb2bd72e307d9007e91c180e25870236","tid":163390,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗太痴身 唔洗特登諗話幫佢做啲咩<br />\n得閒比佢發泄吓<br />\n陪住佢就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實佢而家唔會搵我發洩 佢好似怕左我咁<br />\n可能係我初初 經常說教 佢又唔想聽 <br />\n覺得我都係會話佢做乜轉牛角尖 又唔聽人講咁<br />\n其實我都好後悔 而家我寧願佢會搵我發洩<br />\n但我只想唔好講說話傷害我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233b71acf044ad2c0fcc5af59e396b087131c5d1","tid":163390,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾人姦過！？<br />\n落過仔！？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩樣都唔係"},{"pid":"65aa0f76b03ad874197078022ef219fe87392aa1","tid":163390,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>刺蝟好無食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16da9f8d1fb9c75f5cd3d14b13bce5fb38f36cfb","tid":163390,"uid":1911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"手足頂住"}]}